[SCSI] pm80xx: WWN Modification for PM8081/88/89 controllers

Individual WWN read operations based on controller.
PM8081 - Read WWN from Flash VPD.
PM8088/89 - Read WWN from EEPROM.
PM8001 - Read WWN from NVM.

